      <container name="回顾" eId="container_2">
        <p xml:space="preserve">	<span class="bold">回顾</span>其以往关于苏丹的各项决议，特别是第<a href="https://undocs.org/ch/S/RES/1591(2005)">1591(2005)</a>、<a href="https://undocs.org/ch/S/RES/1651(2005)">1651(2005)</a>、<a href="https://undocs.org/ch/S/RES/1665(2006)">1665(2006)</a>、<a href="https://undocs.org/ch/S/RES/1672(2006)">1672(2006)</a>、<a href="https://undocs.org/ch/S/RES/1713(2006)">1713(2006)</a>、<a href="https://undocs.org/ch/S/RES/1779(2007)">1779(2007)</a>、<a href="https://undocs.org/ch/S/RES/1841(2008)">1841(2008)</a>、<a href="https://undocs.org/ch/S/RES/1891(2009)">1891(2009)</a>、<a href="https://undocs.org/ch/S/RES/1945(2010)">1945(2010)</a>、<a href="https://undocs.org/ch/S/RES/1982(2011)">1982(2011)</a>、<a href="https://undocs.org/ch/S/RES/2035(2012)">2035(2012)</a>、<a href="https://undocs.org/ch/S/RES/2091(2013)">2091(2013)</a>、<a href="https://undocs.org/ch/S/RES/2138(2014)">2138(2014)</a>、<a href="https://undocs.org/ch/S/RES/2200(2015)">2200(2015)</a>、<a href="https://undocs.org/ch/S/RES/2265(2016)">2265(2016)</a>、<a href="https://undocs.org/ch/S/RES/2340(2017)">2340(2017)</a>、<a href="https://undocs.org/ch/S/RES/2400(2018)">2400(2018)</a>、<a href="https://undocs.org/ch/S/RES/2455(2019)">2455(2019)</a>、<a href="https://undocs.org/ch/S/RES/2508(2020)">2508(2020)</a>、<a href="https://undocs.org/ch/S/RES/2562(2021)">2562(2021)</a>、<a href="https://undocs.org/ch/S/RES/2620(2022)">2620(2022)</a>号决议，第<a href="https://undocs.org/ch/S/RES/2664(2022)">2664(2022)</a>、<a href="https://undocs.org/ch/S/RES/2676(2023)">2676(2023)</a>、<a href="https://undocs.org/ch/S/RES/2725(2024)">2725(2024)</a>和<a href="https://undocs.org/ch/S/RES/2736(2024)">2736(2024)</a>号决议补充规定、2018年12月11日安理会主席声明(<a href="https://undocs.org/ch/S/PRST/2018/19">S/PRST/2018/19</a>)以及安理会发表的新闻谈话，并重申对苏丹统一、主权、独立和领土完整的坚定承诺，</p>
      </container>
      <container name="重申" eId="container_3">
        <p xml:space="preserve">	<span class="bold">重申</span>冲突各方必须确保平民得到保护，并促进对侵犯践踏人权行为和违反国际人道法行为的责任追究，</p>
      </container>
      <container name="回顾" eId="container_4">
        <p xml:space="preserve">	<span class="bold">回顾</span>苏丹问题专家小组的最后报告(<a href="https://undocs.org/ch/S/2024/65">S/2024/65</a>)，</p>
      </container>
      <container name="特别指出" eId="container_5">
        <p xml:space="preserve">	<span class="bold">特别指出</span>第1段中回顾的应对达尔富尔局势的措施并非针对苏丹当局，</p>
      </container>
      <container name="表示注意到" eId="container_6">
        <p xml:space="preserve">	<span class="bold">表示注意到</span>秘书长2023年11月24日致安全理事会的信(<a href="https://undocs.org/ch/S/2023/918">S/2023/918</a>)和苏丹政府2023年11月30日致委员会的信(<a href="https://undocs.org/ch/S/AC.47/2023/COMM.8">S/AC.47/2023/COMM.8</a>)，信中提及第<a href="https://undocs.org/ch/S/RES/2676(2023)">2676(2023)</a>号决议第5段，该段要求对安理会第<a href="https://undocs.org/ch/S/RES/2676(2023)">2676(2023)</a>号决议第4段所定关键基准的落实进展进行评估，</p>
      </container>
      <container name="确认" eId="container_7">
        <p xml:space="preserve">	<span class="bold">确认</span>需要维护正当程序并确保有公正而明确的程序用于把根据第<a href="https://undocs.org/ch/S/RES/1591(2005)">1591(2005)</a>号决议和后续决议指认的个人和实体从名单上删除，欢迎通过第<a href="https://undocs.org/ch/S/RES/2744(2024)">2744(2024)</a>号决议，强化除名协调人的任务和程序，</p>
      </container>
      <container name="认定" eId="container_8">
        <p xml:space="preserve">	<span class="bold">认定</span>苏丹局势继续对该区域的国际和平与安全构成威胁，</p>
      </container>
      <container name="采取行动" eId="container_9">
        <p xml:space="preserve">	根据《联合国宪章》第七章<span class="bold">采取行动</span>，</p>
      </container>
